\begin_inset Formula $P_{n}=\sum_{k=0}^{n}\frac{P_{n}^{(k)}(\alpha)}{k!}(x-\alpha)^{k}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
On a aussi 
\begin_inset Formula $P_{n}(x)=\sum_{k=0}^{n}(x-\alpha)^{k}R_{n-k}$
\end_inset

